    <item>
      <title>预计感恩节期间美国各地将出现冬季风暴</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-11-24/forecasts-warn-of-possible-winter-storms-across-us-during-thanksgiving-week</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加利福尼亚州温莎（美联社）——美国各地的气象预报员发出警告，又一轮冬季天气可能给感恩节假期前的旅行带来困难，而加利福尼亚州和华盛顿州仍在继续从风暴破坏和停电中恢复。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-11-24/forecasts-warn-of-possible-winter-storms-across-us-during-thanksgiving-week</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 24 Nov 2024 08:16:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
